    "prompt": "<div>\n<div class=\"stimulus_reference\">\n<div>Which of the following statements best accounts for the fact that the peak on the <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"H e\" role=\"math\"><math alttext=\"H e\" overflow=\"scroll\"> <mstyle> <mrow> <mtext>He</mtext> </mrow> </mstyle> </math></span></span> spectrum is farther to the left and higher than the peak on the <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"H\" role=\"math\"><math alttext=\"H\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>H</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> spectrum?</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n",
    "answer": "i2",
    "choices": [
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"H e\"><math alttext=\"H e\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>He</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> has an additional valence electron in a higher energy level than the valence electron in <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"H\"><math alttext=\"H\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>H</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>.</p>",
        "value": "i1"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"H e\"><math alttext=\"H e\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>He</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> has a greater nuclear charge than <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"H\"><math alttext=\"H\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>H</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> and an additional electron in the same energy level.</p>",
        "value": "i2"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"H e\"><math alttext=\"H e\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>He</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> has a completely filled valence shell in which the electrons are a greater distance from the nucleus than the distance between the <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"H\"><math alttext=\"H\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>H</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> nucleus and its electron.</p>",
        "value": "i3"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">It takes longer for the electrons in <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"H e\"><math alttext=\"H e\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>He</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> to be removed due to the higher nuclear mass of <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"H e\"><math alttext=\"H e\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>He</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>.</p>",
